com.travelbank.knit

Class ViewEvents

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.travelbank.knit.ViewEvents

  • public class ViewEvents
extends java.lang.Object
    A hub for all view events. All view events are fired through this class. Instance is contained inside Knit. Often accessed inside classes annotated with KnitView, Events fired will be received by the KnitPresenter inside the method that is tagged with the associated tag of the ViewEventEnv that is being fired.
